# SpaceAM Ltd

> Designer and manufacturer of ultra-lightweight sensors and flight systems for planetary exploration and defence air-drop missions.

## What they do

SpaceAM develops ultra-lightweight optical sensors, auto-rotating flight systems, and unattended ground sensor capabilities for extreme environments, spanning both interplanetary atmospheric sampling and defence-oriented terrestrial deployment. Their products are patented and designed for air-drop delivery.

## Products and solutions

- **LEVL auto-rotating flight system** - Patented ultra-lightweight autonomous flight system for atmospheric and terrestrial deployment.
- **DarkSeed T-UGS** - Tactical unattended ground sensor capability for defence applications.
- **Ultra-lightweight optical sensors** - Sensors designed for harsh and remote environments including planetary atmospheres.

